{"id": "1465220168245313657", "channel_id": "1465220168245313657", "author_id": "212031841786527764", "author_name": "chinkeeyong", "content": "Just a silly minor bug that probably occurred while implementing the new phantasmal dive changes.\n\nNormally, Uvhash has \"Blood Frenzy\" stacks equal to a percentage of his max hp, so his intention will not change if you don't deal enough damage to remove all Blood Frenzy stacks.\n\nNow, it seems that Uvhash only receives 1 stack of \"Blood Frenzy\", so dealing any damage at all will cause his intention to change and his dialogue line to appear (very annoying when you hit multiple times)", "timestamp": "2026-01-26T05:41:50.584000+00:00", "thread_id": "1465220168245313657", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-26T05:42:35.831000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1465220168572473467", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 366888, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1465220168245313657/1465220168572473467/image.png?ex=69cc075e&is=69cab5de&hm=ba40d0616e65bf1e85a86bdf5935bfc76eada6b169359d8f0357bef7a90757af&"}, {"id": "1465220169109602411", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-01-26_134211.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 564439, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1465220168245313657/1465220169109602411/Screenshot_2026-01-26_134211.png?ex=69cc075e&is=69cab5de&hm=9ea83480f3d31cad9555e124f8c088ccaf6f9b8f4cf662574ee93b99dd27b9c7&"}]}
