{"id": "1465183141223338137", "channel_id": "1465183141223338137", "author_id": "139343733714845697", "author_name": "satachan", "content": "<@633215996508766229> <@1131790839291596841>\n\nAs there is still no communication between the developers to the players regarding how uncertain we feel about absolute axiom.\n\nThis stay tuned dialog has been added to every awakener, even the recently released xu.\n\nPlease give us a clear statement on what your intentions are with absolute axiom existing in the game and what is the developmental direction of morimens from this point on forth.", "timestamp": "2026-01-26T03:14:42.654000+00:00", "thread_id": "1465183141223338137", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-26T03:17:54.680000+00:00", "mentions": ["1131790839291596841", "633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 23}, {"emoji": "Stare", "emoji_id": "1400771552542199902", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1465183142242418948", "filename": "IMG_1144.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1735445, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1465183141223338137/1465183142242418948/IMG_1144.png?ex=69cbe4e2&is=69ca9362&hm=7323df6a60c9f85367194edcfe0d7dd70af79d2238da66dfbd7ab054b6fd58fe&"}]}
{"id": "1465183921091121294", "channel_id": "1465183141223338137", "author_id": "706262934485073951", "author_name": "bagels5899", "content": "To both tease a highly controversial mechanic and release it despite literally the entire fanbase asking you not to speaks volumes \n\ndo not think that just because you *had* goodwill with us means you can do this\n\nyour consumers won’t let you get away with this and I hope your revenue going down will be a good wake up call to all this", "timestamp": "2026-01-26T03:17:48.589000+00:00", "thread_id": "1465183141223338137", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-26T03:17:57.411000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 4}]}
{"id": "1465184886229958852", "channel_id": "1465183141223338137", "author_id": "139343733714845697", "author_name": "satachan", "content": "While as a fellow developer, I know that a patch canmot be taken out in the matters of a few days as development plan and version controls are usually done months in advance.\n\nBut unless we get some form of communication on the direction and plans of morimens or confirmation of non predatory behavior or even the removal of absolute axiom down the line.\n\nThere is currently nothing else but deteriorating good will.\n\nSo please issue to us a proper statement.", "timestamp": "2026-01-26T03:21:38.696000+00:00", "thread_id": "1465183141223338137", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-26T03:22:11.865000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 5}]}
